<div class="text-justify"><span id="VLCPrototyping">Guzm√°n, B. G., Mir, M. S., Fonseca, D. F., Galisteo, A., Wang, Q., &amp; Giustiniano, D. (2023). Prototyping Visible Light Communication for the Internet of Things Using OpenVLC. In <i>IEEE Communications Magazine</i>.</span></div>

