<div class="text-justify"><span id="9079516">Guzm√°n, B. G., Chen, C., Jim√©nez, V. P. G., Haas, H., &amp; Hanzo, L. (2020). Reflection-Based Relaying Techniques in Visible Light Communications: Will it Work? <i>IEEE Access</i>, <i>8</i>, 80922‚Äì80935.</span></div>

