<div id="b10.5555/3400306.3400331" style="display: none; background-color:black; border-radius:5px; padding:10px; margin-bottom:20px;">
<pre>In the near future, the Internet of Things (IoT) will take a predominant role in home automation and a reliable technology must satisfy the high demand on data traffic, energy consumption and reliability. This poster reveals a novel solution for home automation that relies on visible light communication.</pre>
</div>

