<div class="text-justify"><span id="10.1145/3412449.3412552">Mir, M. S., Guzman, B. G., Galisteo, A., &amp; Giustiniano, D. (2020). Non-Linearity of LEDs for VLC IoT Applications. <i>Proceedings of the Workshop on Light Up the IoT Co-Located with ACM MobiCom 2020</i>, 6‚Äì11.</span></div>

