<div class="text-justify"><span id="8238150">Guzman, B. G., Cort√©s, T. M., L√≥pez, √Å. R., &amp; Armada, A. G. (2017). Design of a communication, vision and sensory system for a rescuer robot in coal mine areas. <i>2017 International Conference on Wireless Networks and Mobile Communications (WINCOM)</i>, 1‚Äì5.</span></div>

